{"tid":1500721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[丹麥好波]《羽球世錦賽》諶龍爆冷出局 中國男單全陣亡寫24年來最差成績","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T12:57:56.000Z","uid":282965,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4870c51347fdce292d1a4ff60a0769950dccb4","tid":1500721,"uid":282965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"2019年世界羽球錦標賽，中國男單本屆共4人參賽卻出師不利，繼黃宇翔在64強先買單，陸光祖、林丹也同日在32強落敗，僅存的諶龍稍早出戰世排第9名的丹麥好手安童森（Anders Antonsen），也以20：22、10：21慘遭直落二輸球，中國男單選手在世錦賽也全數出局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2894490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2894490&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=94a8b7cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2894490&h=d02301f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2894490</a>"},{"pid":"54aab2f7d11cc0a7c4eba7f6ff1781f36efa0eea","tid":1500721,"uid":206971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐"},{"pid":"a7b7d01abbc93502f8d064910050375b4f010da7","tid":1500721,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"最勁嗰個石宇奇傷咗無打啫"},{"pid":"8014cb7abdfbe438bb1bfab86e88debf8912f15b","tid":1500721,"uid":149700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b7d01abbc93502f8d064910050375b4f010da7","tid":1500721,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"最勁嗰個石宇奇傷咗無打啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"支那仔收皮la"},{"pid":"f646b231d0e8326663117bcada4e163377ab7067","tid":1500721,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴~~"},{"pid":"e883119386530f61518cd80235de49c1d2ea60a9","tid":1500721,"uid":282965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT